---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import HeroSection from "../components/HeroSection.astro";
import { KEYWORDS } from "../constant";
---

<Layout title="About Our Company - IsMail">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <HeroSection
      title="About IsMail"
      highlightText="IsMail"
      description="We're on a mission to empower businesses with AI driven email marketing."
    />

    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-24">
          <div>
            <span
              class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-secondary-100 dark:bg-secondary-900 text-secondary-600 dark:text-secondary-300 font-medium text-sm mb-4"
            >
              Our Story
            </span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
              From Startup to Industry Leader
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Founded in 2025, {KEYWORDS.name} began with a simple idea: to make
              powerful AI-powered marketing tools accessible to businesses of all
              sizes. What started as a small team of three passionate developers
              has grown into a global company serving thousands of customers worldwide.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Our journey hasn't always been easy, but our commitment to
              innovation, quality, and customer success has remained unwavering.
              Today, we're proud to be recognized as a leader in the AI
              marketing industry, helping businesses transform their operations
              and achieve remarkable results.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              As we continue to grow, we remain dedicated to our core mission:
              empowering businesses with the tools they need to succeed in the
              digital age.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80"
              alt="IsMail Team"
              class="w-full h-auto"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-24">
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <span
              class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-secondary-100 dark:bg-secondary-900 text-secondary-600 dark:text-secondary-300 font-medium text-sm mb-4"
            >
              Our Values
            </span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
              What We Stand For
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
              Our values guide everything we do, from how we build our products
              to how we interact with our customers and each other.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <div
                class="rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-3 w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
              >
                <svg
                  class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3
                class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2"
              >
                Trust & Transparency
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                We believe in building trust through transparency. We're open
                about our processes, pricing, and policies, and we always strive
                to do what's right for our customers.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <div
                class="rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-3 w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
              >
                <svg
                  class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                >
